challenges.description:
In-house sound engineer of Ràdio Ciutat Vella.
Live engineering for most of the programmes, that included cultural magazines, sports, cinema and comedy; ensured the correct functioning of all equipment; created bumpers and promos; general media management such as batch processing, batch renaming, managing backups & recordings;
On own initiative, launched the radio to the internet via a streaming service; assisted creating the official webpage; migrated from a VIVA system to a Sam Broadcaster one, optimizing the workflow and improving the sound quality.
